OL,3,CAbuse victims holding concealed phone
OL,4,Ccan opt out of emergency alert - Long
OL,6,FA loud siren will sound on mobile
OL,7,Fphones this weekend across Northern
OL,8,FIreland, as the government tests its
OL,9,Femergency alert system.
OL,11,FThe emergency alert text will be sent
OL,12,Fat around 3pm on Sunday, September 7,
OL,13,Fin the second-ever nationwide drill.
OL,15,FPhones will vibrate for roughly ten
OL,16,Fseconds - even if they are set to
OL,17,Fsilent - and a message will appear on
OL,18,Fphone screens, making it clear it is a
OL,19,Ftest.
