OL,3,CAbuse victims holding concealed phone
OL,4,Ccan opt out of emergency alert - Long
OL,6,FThe first time the system was tested
OL,7,Fwas in April 2023, but some mobile
OL,8,Fphone users reported that their
OL,9,Fdevices did not sound, with the
OL,10,Fproblem traced to specific networks.
OL,12,FJustice Minister Naomi Long urged
OL,13,Fvictims of abuse to ensure they know
OL,14,Fhow to switch off alerts if they have
OL,15,Fa concealed phone.
OL,17,FThe Justice Minister Naomi Long said:
OL,18,F"I am aware there are people living
OL,19,Funder the shadow of domestic violence
OL,20,Fwho own a second phone which their
OL,21,Fabuser does not know about.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
