OL,6,FThe Emergency Alerts system is an
OL,7,Fimportant tool for reaching the public
OL,8,Fin emergency situations. However, if
OL,9,Fyou need to turn off these alerts the
OL,10,Fgovernment advice on how to switch off
OL,11,Fthe alert is:
OL,13,FiPhoneJTo opt out:
OL,15,FGo to your settings and select the
OL,16,F'notifications' menu.JScroll to the
OL,17,Fbottom.JTurn off 'severe alerts' and
OL,18,F'extreme alerts'.
OL,20,FAndroid phonesJTo opt out:
